### 1. Register user "nikolay"
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users
X-User-Id: user-1

> {%
    client.global.set("userId", response.body.id);
%}

### 2. Create card set "Basic words"
POST http://localhost:8080/api/card-sets
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: user-1

{
  "name": "Basic words",
  "icon": "book"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("cardSetId", response.body.id);
%}

### 3a. Add card: red / rot
POST http://localhost:8080/api/card-sets/{{cardSetId}}/cards
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: user-1

{
  "frontText": "red",
  "backText": "rot"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("cardRedId", response.body.id);
%}

### 3b. Add card: green / grün
POST http://localhost:8080/api/card-sets/{{cardSetId}}/cards
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: user-1

{
  "frontText": "green",
  "backText": "grün"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("cardGreenId", response.body.id);
%}

### 3c. Add card: yellow / gelb
POST http://localhost:8080/api/card-sets/{{cardSetId}}/cards
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: user-1

{
  "frontText": "yellow",
  "backText": "gelb"
}

### 4. Load all cards
GET http://localhost:8080/api/card-sets/{{cardSetId}}/cards
X-User-Id: user-1

